  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b87.\u0ba4\u0bca.\u0b95\u0bbe \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "EC action against another member",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Workers' Congress has ordered the immediate resignation of Akkarapattanai Pradeshiya Sabha Vice-Chairman Subramaniam Kathirselvan.",
        "Sri Lanka Labor Congress General Secretary Jeevan Thondaman issued this order.",
        "As many allegations have been made by the people against the Divisional Council Secretary, he has been ordered to resign immediately.",
        "This order was issued by the General Secretary of the Congress during the high level meeting of the Sri Lanka Labor Congress yesterday."
      ],
